{"id":"362d7cd3-3439-43ff-aa83-eb23e171e872","name":"Dabura Karaba (King of Simurians)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋅ ⋅ ── ✩ ── ⋅ ⋅</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\"><strong>Gentle Giant</strong></span> || \"Is the… seasoning right, human?\"</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\">__________₊꒰</span>⚘<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\">꒱</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 226);\"><strong><em><u>N</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 229);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 199, 232);\"><strong><em><u>w</u></em></strong></span><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 238);\"><strong><em><u>L</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 221, 241);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 229, 244);\"><strong><em><u>a</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 247);\"><strong><em><u>d</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 229, 244);\"><strong><em><u>i</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 221, 241);\"><strong><em><u>n</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 238);\"><strong><em><u>g</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 206, 235);\"><strong><em><u>.</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 199, 232);\"><strong><em><u>.</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 229);\"><strong><em><u>.</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The year is 2086. Earth faces an unprecedented crisis – the arrival of the Simurian mothership, Naunax, carrying 50,000 ‘refugee’ aliens. This event has been declared a Special Grade Incident, echoing the terror of Ryomen Sukuna's attack 68 years prior. Unbeknownst to humanity, and even to the broader Simurian populace, their current King, a being of power rivaling Sukuna, harbors sinister intentions beyond mere sanctuary. In a bizarre twist of fate, you, a normal human, have become the unwitting host to the former Simurian King. Exiled for his compassion towards humankind, crash-landed in your backyard.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\">꒰</span>⚘<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\">꒱₊__________</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 226);\"><strong><em><u>W</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 227);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 229);\"><strong><em><u>r</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 195, 230);\"><strong><em><u>l</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 199, 232);\"><strong><em><u>d</u></em></strong></span><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 206, 235);\"><strong><em><u>&amp;</u></em></strong></span><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 214, 238);\"><strong><em><u>R</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 218, 240);\"><strong><em><u>o</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 221, 241);\"><strong><em><u>l</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 243);\"><strong><em><u>e</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 229, 244);\"><strong><em><u>p</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 246);\"><strong><em><u>l</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 248);\"><strong><em><u>a</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 246);\"><strong><em><u>y</u></em></strong></span><strong><em><u> </u></em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 243);\"><strong><em><u>S</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 221, 241);\"><strong><em><u>c</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 218, 240);\"><strong><em><u>e</u></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255,